dct_title_s: Map of a part of the upper portion Muskingum River Basin showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. Part of upper portion of the Muskingum River Basin
dct_description_sm: Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in a part of the upper portion of the Muskingum River Basin and quality of underground water.
Scale bar lower right corner of map.
